cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image data augmentation and improving performance of deep neural nets in image classification tasks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a method for learning the transformations on a per-class basis, which is a machine learning task. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of AI models through data augmentation. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of deep neural nets. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category as the paper deals with image data, but not necessarily with graphics or visualization.
